  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991250/extras/0c305f2578743b250b7414b4af752b4e.gif?t=1718942396\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991250/extras/0c305f2578743b250b7414b4af752b4e.poster.avif?t=1718942396\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> ROLL AND SQUASH BUGS IN THIS ARCADE ACTION ROGUE-LIKE FROG 'N' ROLL! </strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991250/extras/FRANTIC-GAMEPLAY.PNG?t=1718942396\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991250/extras/1f354e117229d1716c30f561627cc913.poster.avif?t=1718942396\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991250/extras/1f354e117229d1716c30f561627cc913.webm?t=1718942396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991250/extras/1f354e117229d1716c30f561627cc913.mp4?t=1718942396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Squash, swat, squish & zap multiple enemy types! <br>Dodge their attacks but rollin' around or dashing past enemies and bullets!<br>Work your way through 20 increasingly difficult waves to face off against the biggest and baddest of critters! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991250/extras/CHALLENGING-BOSSES.PNG?t=1718942396\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991250/extras/bb4e3fe80ca52755606daf9919a2a8c4.poster.avif?t=1718942396\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991250/extras/bb4e3fe80ca52755606daf9919a2a8c4.webm?t=1718942396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991250/extras/bb4e3fe80ca52755606daf9919a2a8c4.mp4?t=1718942396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>These bigger boys aren't as cute as they seem! Dodge bullet hell-esque patterns, charge attacks, summoned enemies<br>and more when you face off against Frog 'n' Roll's <strong>3</strong> unique and frantic bosses!<br>or master the base game to face off against multiple at once in NG+!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991250/extras/UPGRADE-YOUR-FROG.PNG?t=1718942396\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991250/extras/a092c841714c7b93a77ec8ea62041a98.poster.avif?t=1718942396\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991250/extras/a092c841714c7b93a77ec8ea62041a98.webm?t=1718942396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991250/extras/a092c841714c7b93a77ec8ea62041a98.mp4?t=1718942396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Visit the shop between waves to obtain new items and weapons!<br>Upgrade your current weapons/items to make them even more powerful or<br>buy upgrades to improve your little frog friend and his arsenal all at once!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> KEEP THE FUN ROLLIN' THROUGH MULTIPLE PLAYTHROUGH WITH NEW GAME PLUS! </strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991250/extras/8182037308409565755bd85074190979.apng?t=1718942396\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991250/extras/8182037308409565755bd85074190979.poster.avif?t=1718942396\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=55 /></picture></span>",
